DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL
v.
CLUTTS 2018-1227 Supreme Court of Ohio. September 27, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

On certified order of the Supreme Court of Illinois, No. 2017PR00048.

Raymond Edward Clutts, Attorney Registration No. 0058842, last known address in Schaumburg, Illinois, suspended from the practice of law in Ohio for three years.
